at the studio.

706
00:33:39,684 --> 00:33:41,948
Oh...

707
00:33:41,986 --> 00:33:43,453
We had no business there.

708
00:33:43,488 --> 00:33:47,219
Well, l hope you'll both come
and make a real tour...

