00:37:29,513 --> 00:37:31,640
Talk?

766
00:37:31,682 --> 00:37:32,671
Mm-hmm.

767
00:37:32,716 --> 00:37:35,651
l don't think you people
read things.

768
00:37:35,686 --> 00:37:36,653
The men...

769
00:37:36,687 --> 00:37:39,121
