one of them falls into a well

772
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:45,754
and has to be hauled up...

773
00:37:45,796 --> 00:37:47,525
in a bucket.

774
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:51,891
Would you write that
in a book of your own?

775
00:37:51,935 --> 00:37:54,495
