all day.

789
00:38:18,462 --> 00:38:19,486
You're exhausted.

790
00:38:21,465 --> 00:38:23,729
This is you.

791
00:38:26,770 --> 00:38:28,397
A girl comes in.

792
00:38:45,589 --> 00:38:47,181
She doesn't see you.

793
00:38:49,993 --> 00:38:51,517
