in the room...

816
00:40:06,136 --> 00:40:09,435
watching every move
the girl makes.

817
00:40:41,472 --> 00:40:42,837
What happens?

818
00:40:43,974 --> 00:40:44,941
l don't know.

819
00:40:44,975 --> 00:40:46,840
l was just making pictures.

820
00:40:48,312 --> 00:40:49,540
